description: Best practices for using Tailwind CSS
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx,css}
---

- Use utility-first approach for styling components
- Create custom components for frequently used styles
- Utilize responsive design utilities for different screen sizes
- Keep your `tailwind.config.js` organized and maintainable
- Use @apply directives sparingly and only for reusable styles
- Implement proper dark mode support using Tailwind's dark: variant
- Follow mobile-first design principles
- Use arbitrary values only when necessary 